overview:
Built Right LLC is a multi-service company providing expertise in home improvement and repair.

We provide general contractor and handyman services including drywall, painting, installation (doors, windows, appliances, and cabinetry), and remodeling. Built Right LLC is dedicated to helping our customers in the Pierce and Thurston County areas of Washington make their homes a beautiful and wonderful place to live.

Through the direction and efforts of Joel Englund, who brings over 15 years of experience in the construction and general contracting industries, we have been serving a diverse clientele in the Puget Sound area of Western Washington with pride. Built Right focuses on delivering quality services with the flexibility to meet clients’ specific needs. Our customer base includes repeat business, referrals, and new clients. We service both site-built and manufactured (prefabricated, mobile, and modular) homes. No job is too small for us.
